# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:13
translate portuguese jamietv2_fd039b16:

    # "I walk up to Jamie's door and knock."
    "aproximo-me da porta da Jamie e bato."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:14
translate portuguese jamietv2_fdad75c4:

    # "I wait a bit for her to answer and after a few moments, I almost walk away thinking that she isn't home or is busy or something."
    "Espero um pouco que ela responda e, passados alguns instantes, quase me vou embora, pensando que ela não está em casa ou está ocupada ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:19
translate portuguese jamietv2_56b288a0:

    # "Then, just when I am about to leave, she opens the door."
    "Então, mesmo quando estou prestes a sair, ela abre a porta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:20
translate portuguese jamietv2_348b659c:

    # gnd "Hey sorry, I must have fell asleep on the couch."
    gnd "Olá, desculpa, devo ter adormecido no sofá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:21
translate portuguese jamietv2_85e15039:

    # pc "Oh I'm sorry, I didn't mean to wake you. Was just wondering if you wanted to hang out?"
    pc "Oh, desculpa, não queria acordar-te. Só estava a pensar se te apetecia sair um bocadinho?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:22
translate portuguese jamietv2_8cddc873:

    # gnd "Sure, want to come watch TV with me?"
    gnd "Claro, queres vir ver televisão comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:23
translate portuguese jamietv2_6eafa1e5:

    # pc "Are you sure? You look pretty tired."
    pc "Tens a certeza? Pareces bastante cansada."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:24
translate portuguese jamietv2_d5f53ad3:

    # gnd "I'm exhausted, but I'd still like to spend some time with you."
    gnd "Estou exausta, mas mesmo assim gostava de passar algum tempo contigo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:25
translate portuguese jamietv2_35743d5e:

    # pc "Okay then."
    pc "Está bem, então."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:26
translate portuguese jamietv2_d6443097:

    # "We walk inside and sit down on her couch to watch TV together."
    "Entramos e sentamo-nos no sofá dela para ver televisão juntos."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:29
translate portuguese jamietv2_4eefcd41:

    # pc "You not been sleeping well?"
    pc "Não tens dormido bem?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:30
translate portuguese jamietv2_d3a1e5f8:

    # gnd "I've just been studying a lot. It's been tough."
    gnd "Tenho estudado muito. Tem sido difícil."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:31
translate portuguese jamietv2_6d7e76b4:

    # pc "Tell me about it."
    pc "Nem me digas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:32
translate portuguese jamietv2_56872787:

    # gnd "But I'm glad to spend some time with you, even if I'm sleepy."
    gnd "Mas fico contente por passar algum tempo contigo, mesmo que esteja com sono."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:37
translate portuguese jamietv2_c7a75159:

    # gnd "Are you implying I'm not cute when I'm not sleepy?"
    gnd "Estás a insinuar que não sou gira quando não estou com sono?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:38
translate portuguese jamietv2_4db958a5:

    # pc "What? No."
    pc "O quê? Não."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:39
translate portuguese jamietv2_cf0825c6:

    # gnd "I'm just kidding. Thanks, you're sweet."
    gnd "Estou só a brincar. Obrigada, és querido."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:42
translate portuguese jamietv2_175d3768:

    # gnd "What? Are you serious?"
    gnd "O quê? Estás a falar a sério?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:43
translate portuguese jamietv2_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:44
translate portuguese jamietv2_f3a7bdd3:

    # gnd "That's probably not a good idea. My dad might actually kill you."
    gnd "Isso provavelmente não é uma boa ideia. O meu pai pode até matar-te."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:45
translate portuguese jamietv2_796397b3:

    # pc "It might be worth the risk."
    pc "Talvez valha a pena correr o risco."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:46
translate portuguese jamietv2_34f266ea:

    # gnd "You're crazy!"
    gnd "És louco!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:49
translate portuguese jamietv2_d13864ee:

    # gnd "But no, let's just watch TV."
    gnd "Mas não, vamos apenas ver televisão."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:52
translate portuguese jamietv2_8105064d:

    # "She smiles at me and we both turn towards the TV and watch the show."
    "Ela sorri para mim e ambos nos viramos para a televisão e vemos o programa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:55
translate portuguese jamietv2_e4b4fe92:

    # "After the first commercial break, I hear her snoring softly and a moment later, she leans over and lays her head on my shoulder."
    "Após o primeiro intervalo publicitário, ouço-a a ressonar baixinho e, um momento depois, ela inclina-se e deita a cabeça no meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:56
translate portuguese jamietv2_72d126bc:

    # "I sit there like that, feeling her warm weight against me, smelling the scent of her shampoo. It's nice."
    "Fico ali sentado assim, a sentir o seu peso quente contra mim, a cheirar o aroma do seu champô. É bom."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:57
translate portuguese jamietv2_a7276863:

    # "I watch the rest of the show, letting her sleep on my shoulder until the credits roll."
    "Vejo o resto do programa, deixando-a dormir no meu ombro até aos créditos finais."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:60
translate portuguese jamietv2_aced7ae5:

    # "The music playing during the credits wakes her and she opens her eyes and looks up at me, putting her hand on my chest."
    "A música que toca durante os créditos acorda-a e ela abre os olhos e olha para mim, colocando a mão no meu peito."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:61
translate portuguese jamietv2_222fe902:

    # gnd "Oh man, I missed the whole thing."
    gnd "Caramba, perdi tudo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:62
translate portuguese jamietv2_7289beae:

    # pc "Yeah, I'll have to fill you in later."
    pc "Sim, vou ter de te contar tudo mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:63
translate portuguese jamietv2_d912edc5:

    # gnd "You could have woke me up."
    gnd "Podias ter-me acordado."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:66
translate portuguese jamietv2_fd8175bb:

    # gnd "I definitely did."
    gnd "E acordei, sem dúvida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:68
translate portuguese jamietv2_7b910158:

    # gnd "You're so silly."
    gnd "És tão tolo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:69
translate portuguese jamietv2_d404c590:

    # gnd "Do you really think I'm cute?"
    gnd "Achas mesmo que sou gira?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:70
translate portuguese jamietv2_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "Sem dúvida."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:71
translate portuguese jamietv2_d2d7ae9c:

    # gnd "I think you're cute too."
    gnd "Também acho que és gira."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:72
translate portuguese jamietv2_e8e9a7f7:

    # "Once again, her dad picks the worst moment to open the door and walk in."
    "Mais uma vez, o pai dela escolhe o pior momento para abrir a porta e entrar."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:73
translate portuguese jamietv2_9da07a83:

    # "Jamie leans away from me and stands up."
    "A Jamie afasta-se de mim e levanta-se."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:79
translate portuguese jamietv2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_011.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:80
translate portuguese jamietv2_25b98dfa:

    # gnd "Hey, Daddy."
    gnd "Olá, papá."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:81
translate portuguese jamietv2_20dcad47:

    # jd "Send him home."
    jd "Manda-o para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:82
translate portuguese jamietv2_f2596c67:

    # "Her dad doesn't say anything else and instead walks past us and into the kitchen."
    "O pai dela não diz mais nada e, em vez disso, passa por nós e entra na cozinha."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:86
translate portuguese jamietv2_84d4365c:

    # gnd "He must have had a bad day."
    gnd "Ele deve ter tido um dia mau."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:87
translate portuguese jamietv2_b44cf649:

    # pc "I should probably go."
    pc "Provavelmente devo ir-me embora."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:88
translate portuguese jamietv2_a6870bf2:

    # gnd "Yeah, I'm sorry."
    gnd "Sim, desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:89
translate portuguese jamietv2_b219d344:

    # pc "It's okay."
    pc "Não faz mal."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:92
translate portuguese jamietv2_36b8ae4f:

    # gnd "Thanks for coming over tonight. I had a good time."
    gnd "Obrigada por teres vindo esta noite. Diverti-me imenso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:93
translate portuguese jamietv2_041dfd87:

    # pc "More like you had a good nap."
    pc "Mais parece que tiraste uma boa sesta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:94
translate portuguese jamietv2_b762e00f:

    # gnd "That too. Your shoulder is very comfy."
    gnd "Isso também. O teu ombro é muito confortável."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:98
translate portuguese jamietv2_4bbcc4b9:

    # gnd "I might take you up on that."
    gnd "Talvez aproveite essa oferta."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:100
translate portuguese jamietv2_f9097bdf:

    # gnd "I'm sure they'll show re-runs all week."
    gnd "Tenho a certeza de que vão passar repetições a semana toda."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:101
translate portuguese jamietv2_dfc3c586:

    # pc "Alright, well I better head home."
    pc "Tudo bem, é melhor eu ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:103
translate portuguese jamietv2_ecb1e778:

    # gnd "Okay, [pcname]. See you again soon."
    gnd "Ok, [pcname]. Até breve."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:104
translate portuguese jamietv2_209b1712:

    # pc "See ya."
    pc "Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieTV/jamietv2.rpy:105
translate portuguese jamietv2_1557defd:

    # "With that, she goes back inside and I walk back over to my house."
    "Dito isto, ela volta para dentro e eu caminho de volta para a minha casa."

